The Muddy Pro-Cam 10 delivers crystal clear video and still imagery of wildlife, wilderness, and natural habitats day and night. Provides excellent, high-quality 10MP full color daytime photos and 2MP monochrome nighttime photos using Invisible Flash with 18 HE LEDs at a trigger speed of 1.5 seconds. Optional 2-6 photo burst with 2 seconds interval.
